<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>外币付商城</title>
    <style>
        html { font-family:"Microsoft YaHei",Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif,"宋体"; font-size:14px; height: 100%;}
        *{margin: 0;padding: 0;}
        .table-box{width: 536px;margin: 0 auto;margin-top: 40px;padding:30px 30px 60px 30px;border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;}
        .table-box .tips{color: #b8b8b8;}
        .header-box{text-align: center;}
        .word-box{margin-top:20px; }
        .word-box p{padding:10px 0;line-height:2.5;letter-spacing: 2px}
        .word-box p.my-word{text-indent:32px;}
        .word-box p.name{padding-bottom: 0;}
        .word-box  a{text-decoration: none;}
        .word-box  a:hover{text-decoration: underline;}
        .word-box p .web-address{color: #3a9be2;}
        .word-box p .order-num{color: #ffbe67;}


        .word-box table{margin-top: 20px;width: 100%;text-align: center;line-height: 1.5;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;border-left:0}
        .word-box table thead{color: #000;font-weight: normal;}
        .word-box table tr td,.word-box table th {padding:10px;}
        .word-box table tr td{border-left:1px solid #ccc;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5}
        .word-box table th{border-left:1px solid #e5e5e5;background-color:#f2f2f2; }
        .word-box table tr.odd{background-color: #fff;}
        .word-box table tr.even{background-color: #f2f2f2;}
        .word-box .copyright{margin-top: 30px;text-align: center;}

        .statement-box{width: 600px;margin:0 auto;margin-top: 30px;text-align: center;background-color: #fffff7;}
        .statement-box p{padding: 25px;border: 1px dashed #ccc;}
        .statement-box .action{cursor: pointer;color: #f00;}
        .statement-box .action:hover{color:  #3a9be2;}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="table-box">
        <div class="header-box">
            <img src="http://waibifu.com/assets/img/logo.png" alt="" />
        </div>
        <div class="word-box">
            <p>亲爱的商城用户：</p>
		    <p class="my-word">
                您曾经购买的商品（<a href="http://www.waibifu.com/@cardType" class="order-num">@cardName </a>））已经补货完毕，您可以放心继续购买。我们为当时商品缺货的突发情况表达歉意。非常感谢您一直对外币付商城的支持，祝您生活愉快。
            </p>
            <p class="tips">此邮件为自动发送，无需回复。</p>
            <div class="copyright">
                © 2017 <a href="waibifu.com"></a> 外币付商城 版权所有
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>